Title: Brand X
Plot: While protecting a man due to testify against the Morley cigarette company, Skinner is horrified when the witness dies mysteriously. What the agents soon discover is that a new brand of cigarette has a dangerous secret.
GuestStars: Arthur Rosenberg, Ron Marasco, Pat Destro, Caryn West, Rick Deats, David Sawyer, Greg Poland, Matthew T. Wilson, Dennis Boutsikaris, Tobin Bell, Shannon O'Hurley, Richard Cox
